{"tid":1800792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【前新聞主播梁凱寧】聖誕大晒黑絲超養眼 女神聖誕願望：留給香港","createTime":"2019-12-28T07:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T08:17:26.000Z","uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3983144bd8fb5be5ebe92e740bb529bb1620de","tid":1800792,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"【前新聞主播梁凱寧】聖誕大晒黑絲超養眼 <br />\n女神聖誕願望：留給香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日的聖誕，不知你過得快樂嗎？有不少人會選擇靜靜跟愛侶、家人渡過，也有人會選擇跟一大班朋友開Party、酒會。至於前新聞主播梁凱寧 (Maggie)，離開大台3個月後，也不忘本，相約以前的舊同事慶祝！<span style=\"color: red;\">Maggie以一身紅衣短褲，配襯誘人黑絲，夠節日氣氛之餘，還相當養眼</span>，不愧是「最想一起過聖誕的女朋友」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裸辭的勇氣<br />\n27歲的Maggie，自2013年加入大台做主播之後，一做就做了6年，在今年9月1日於大氣電波留下：「新聞報道完，多謝支持，各位再見。」就正式辭職。觀眾雖然不捨，但如果了解Maggie多一點的話，其實也會替她能下這個決定而感到驕傲，畢竟有能力的人，留在大台終究也是一種浪費。"},{"pid":"d34c5b3d047146d584866ca2a23a729a7982b322","tid":1800792,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"moto？"},{"pid":"9c3e415711f298065ef5defb1438eea6750c27d5","tid":1800792,"uid":15,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"9998f4424e130c3b7d3e073ac15ba00f6bd7dae1","tid":1800792,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"？？"},{"pid":"c520d6a7a29fba69f7e05670890e90894392bd25","tid":1800792,"uid":96767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"圖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53cde162d1842614db121e04f4ab5bd2e20cfcd","tid":1800792,"uid":324246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"揾人救救樓主老母"},{"pid":"8ed7229fed540dfe2120a238fc4c30314dce5337","tid":1800792,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"救樓主老母：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/people/women-we-love/MaggieLeung-Christmas-SexyinBlack\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2FMaggieLeung-Christmas-SexyinBlack&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPL9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=9bfdf698\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.esquirehk.com/people/women-we-love/MaggieLeung-Christmas-SexyinBlack</a>"},{"pid":"5e38eace000740539c07fadadeb92d00a7f8316d","tid":1800792,"uid":100550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"315ea6a4ed67d84f95d7b8786dacf9d7827e4815","tid":1800792,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnMoJOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnMoJOw.jpg&h=771c75d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9292880e3afb0b7a9d2733e4a187c2f89a9d01d6","tid":1800792,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1d3983144bd8fb5be5ebe92e740bb529bb1620de","tid":1800792,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"【前新聞主播梁凱寧】聖誕大晒黑絲超養眼 <br />\n女神聖誕願望：留給香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日的聖誕，不知你過得快樂嗎？有不少人會選擇靜靜跟愛侶、家人渡過，也有人會選擇跟一大班朋友開Party、酒會。至於前新聞主播梁凱寧 (Maggie)，離開大台3個月後，也不忘本，相約以前的舊同事慶祝！<span style=\"color: red;\">Maggie以一身紅衣短褲，配襯誘人黑絲，夠節日氣氛之餘，還相當養眼</span>，不愧是「最想一起過聖誕的女朋友」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裸辭的勇氣<br />\n27歲的Maggie，自2013年加入大台做主播之後，一做就做了6年，在今年9月1日於大氣電波留下：「新聞報道完，多謝支持，各位再見。」就正式辭職。觀眾雖然不捨，但如果了解Maggie多一點的話，其實也會替她能下這個決定而感到驕傲，畢竟有能力的人，留在大台終究也是一種浪費。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/maggieleung-christmas-sexyinblack/screenshot-2019-12-26-at-2-56-32-pm/3419088-1-chi-HK/Screenshot-2019-12-26-At-2-56-32-PM_img_1032_688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeop